query:
-- Insert distributor record for Dakota Rea
INSERT INTO distributors (
  userId,
  distributorCode,
  sponsorId,
  placementParentId,
  placementPosition,
  rank,
  personalSales,
  teamSales,
  leftLegVolume,
  rightLegVolume,
  totalEarnings,
  availableBalance,
  monthlyPV,
  monthlyAutoshipPV,
  activeDownlineCount,
  isActive,
  status,
  country,
  createdAt,
  updatedAt
) 
SELECT 
  id as userId,
  'DIST00001' as distributorCode,
  NULL as sponsorId,
  NULL as placementParentId,
  NULL as placementPosition,
  'starter' as rank,
  0 as personalSales,
  0 as teamSales,
  0 as leftLegVolume,
  0 as rightLegVolume,
  0 as totalEarnings,
  0 as availableBalance,
  0 as monthlyPV,
  0 as monthlyAutoshipPV,
  0 as activeDownlineCount,
  1 as isActive,
  'active' as status,
  'US' as country,
  NOW() as createdAt,
  NOW() as updatedAt
FROM users 
WHERE name = 'Dakota Rea' 
LIMIT 1;
